{"tid":1124943,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Fit 登陸 IOS 平台　不再 Android 專享　","createTime":"2019-04-25T10:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T13:53:52.000Z","uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdc64ac879934eed7b56cd5a894091c7d6a5b16","tid":1124943,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"相信不少人做運動時都會用手機程式記錄身體狀況，而如果大家是 iPhone 用戶的話就有好消息了，因為 Google 的健身程式 Google Fit 現已登陸 iOS 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Fit 於 2014 年於 Android 平台推出，並在去年更新介面，而現在該程式亦已登陸 iOS。界面與 Android 版相似，且可與 Nike Run Club、Sleep Cycle 和 Headspace 手機程式的數抓同步，從而收集運動數據。用戶亦可將 Apple Watch 或 Wear OS 的裝置連接到 Google Fit。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Fit 內有活動時間和心肺強化分數兩種目標，該些建議是由世界衛生組織訂定，而 Google Fit 可串連其他手機程式收集數據，分析每日的運動是否達標。此外，Google Fit 亦會提供其他運動建議改善用戶健康。<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/25/googlefitios/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2Fgooglefitios%2Fsoftware%2F&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=2d419615\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/25/googlefitios/software/</a>"},{"pid":"4914b4c6d8555fad5c06d2c50b3f716d0a8c6fe6","tid":1124943,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cdc64ac879934eed7b56cd5a894091c7d6a5b16","tid":1124943,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"相信不少人做運動時都會用手機程式記錄身體狀況，而如果大家是 iPhone 用戶的話就有好消息了，因為 Google 的健身程式 Google Fit 現已登陸 iOS 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Fit 於 2014 年於 Android 平台推出，並在去年更新介面，而現在該程式亦已登陸 iOS。界面與 Android 版相似，且可與 Nike Run Club、Sleep Cycle 和 Headspace 手機程式的數抓同步，從而收集運動數據。用戶亦可將 Apple Watch 或 Wear OS 的裝置連接到 Google Fit。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Fit 內有活動時間和心肺強化分數兩種目標，該些建議是由世界衛生組織訂定，而 Google Fit 可串連其他手機程式收集數據，分析每日的運動是否達標。此外，Google Fit 亦會提供其他運動建議改善用戶健康。<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/25/googlefitios/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2Fgooglefitios%2Fsoftware%2F&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=2d419615\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/25/googlefitios/software/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://propagandaposterstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpropagandaposterstore.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2F001.jpg&h=cf3bf375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle bid data want you<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471993e075a2bb5514c09be155b8686cb6d0d0a2","tid":1124943,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"其實有人會用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bc89fc0737ca1873962c2e4bdc1e2607cb6983","tid":1124943,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"有幾多傻鳩會iPhone+android錶？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢度有個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a60ca60a19a326220910e47b8637026e642b56","tid":1124943,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89bc89fc0737ca1873962c2e4bdc1e2607cb6983","tid":1124943,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"有幾多傻鳩會iPhone+android錶？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢度有個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"圓錶面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}